description: Construction of a part four, part five and part six storey development to provide a total of 115 apartments in the southern part of the site on location of former 'Mill' Building (Amendment to planning permission reference 2006/0064, to replace Building 4) as shown on drawing Nos. 1 -19 (inclusive) received 5 December 2007 and accommodation schedule revision C (reference to Blocks 4, 9 and 10) received 17 January 2008.
